2.A

\[ + \infty \]

 

2.B

1

 

2.C

0

 

2.D

\[ - \infty \]

Đáp án

C

chi tiết

\[\lim \left( {\sqrt {2{n^2} + 3} - n\sqrt 2 } \right) = \lim \frac{{2{n^2} + 3 - 2{n^2}}}{{\sqrt {2{n^2} + 3} + n\sqrt 2 }}\]\[ = \lim \frac{3}{{\sqrt {2{n^2} + 3} + n\sqrt 2 }} = 0\]

1.b

Tính giới hạn :

\[\lim \frac{{\sqrt {{n^2} + 3} - \sqrt {2n + 1} }}{{2 - n}}\]

 

2.A

-1

 

2.B

0

 

2.C

\[ + \infty \]

 

2.D

\[ - \infty \]

 

3.Đáp án

A

 

4.Đáp án chi tiết

\[\lim \frac{{\sqrt {{n^2} + 3} - \sqrt {2n + 1} }}{{2 - n}} = \lim \frac{{\sqrt {1 + \frac{3}{{{n^2}}}} - \sqrt {\frac{2}{n} + \frac{1}{{{n^2}}}} }}{{\frac{2}{n} - 1}} = \frac{1}{{ - 1}} = - 1\]

c

Kết quả của

\[\lim \left( {n - \sqrt {2{n^2} + 2} } \right)\]

 

2.A

\[ - \infty \]

 

2.B

\[ + \infty \]

 

2.C

0

 

2.D

-1

 

3.Đáp án

A

 

4.Đáp án chi tiết

\[\lim \left( {n - \sqrt {2{n^2} + 2} } \right) = \lim \frac{{{n^2} - 2{n^2} - 2}}{{n + \sqrt {2{n^2} + 2} }} = \lim \frac{{ - {n^2} - 2}}{{n + \sqrt {2{n^2} + 2} }}\]

\[ = \lim \frac{{ - n - \frac{2}{n}}}{{1 + \sqrt {2 + \frac{2}{{{n^2}}}} }} = - \infty \]

\[ - \infty \]

\[ + \infty \]

\[\lim \frac{{\sqrt {{n^3} - 1} + \sqrt {{n^3} + 2} }}{{n + 1}} = \lim \frac{{\sqrt {1 - \frac{1}{{{n^3}}}} + \sqrt {1 + \frac{2}{{{n^3}}}} }}{{{n^{\frac{{ - 1}}{2}}} + {n^{ - \frac{3}{2}}}}} = \lim \frac{2}{{\frac{1}{{\sqrt n }} + \frac{1}{{\sqrt {{n^3}} }}}} = \frac{2}{0} = + \infty \]

1.f

Tính

\[\lim \frac{{\sqrt {{n^2} + 2} - \sqrt {2 + n + {n^2}} }}{{\sqrt {{n^2} + 1} }}\]

:

 

2.A

\[ - \infty \]

 

2.B

1

 

2.C

0

 

2.D

\[ + \infty \]

 

3.Đáp án

C

 

4.Đáp án chi tiết

\[\begin{gathered}

\lim \frac{{\sqrt {{n^2} + 2} - \sqrt {2 + n + {n^2}} }}{{\sqrt {{n^2} + 1} }} = \lim \frac{{ - n}}{{\sqrt {{n^2} + 1} \left( {\sqrt {{n^2} + 2} + \sqrt {2 + n + {n^2}} } \right)}} \hfill \\

= \lim \frac{{\frac{{ - 1}}{n}}}{{\sqrt {1 + \frac{1}{{{n^2}}}} \left( {\sqrt {1 + \frac{2}{{{n^2}}}} + \sqrt {\frac{2}{{{n^2}}} + \frac{1}{n} + 1} } \right)}} = 0 \hfill \\

\end{gathered} \]

\[ - \infty \]

\[\lim \left( {\sqrt {2{n^2} + 1} - \sqrt {{n^2} + 2} } \right) = \lim \frac{{2{n^2} + 1 - {n^2} - 2}}{{\sqrt {2{n^2} + 1} + \sqrt {{n^2} + 2} }} = \lim \frac{{{n^2} - 1}}{{\sqrt {2{n^2} + 1} + \sqrt {{n^2} + 2} }}\]

\[ = \lim \frac{{n - \frac{1}{n}}}{{\sqrt {2 + \frac{1}{{{n^2}}}} + \sqrt {1 + \frac{2}{{{n^2}}}} }} = + \infty \]
